# Vaultix SQLite Data Schema

This project uses a SQLite schema compatible with Money Manager `.mmbak` files. The schema is created by `mmbak-export.service` and expected by `mmbak-import.service`.

## Tables Overview

- **ASSETGROUP**: Wallet groups (cash, bank, card, etc.).
- **ASSETS**: Wallet/accounts used in Vaultix.
- **CURRENCY**: Supported currencies and rates.
- **ZCATEGORY**: Income/expense/transfer categories.
- **INOUTCOME**: All transactions (income, expense, transfer).
- **TAG**: Tags attached to transactions.
- **TX_TAG**: Many-to-many link between transactions and tags.
- **BUDGET** / **BUDGET_AMOUNT**: Budget definitions and per-period amounts.
- **REPEATTRANSACTION**: Recurring transactions.
- **FAVTRANSACTION**: Favorite/quick transactions.
- **MEMO**: Notes/memos.
- **ZETC**: Miscellaneous configuration / extra data.
- **PHOTO**: Attachments related to transactions.
- **android_metadata**: Locale metadata (`en_US`).

## Table Details

### ASSETGROUP

- **Primary key**: `DEVICE_ID` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT, unique via `UNIQUE_IDX_ASSETGROUP_UID`)
- **Important columns**:
  - `ACC_GROUP_NAME` (group name)
  - `TYPE` (group type, mapped to wallet group type)
  - `ORDERSEQ` (ordering)
  - `IS_DEL` (soft delete flag)

### ASSETS

- **Primary key**: `ID` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT, unique via `UNIQUE_IDX_ASSETS_UID`)
- **Core columns**:
  - `NIC_NAME` (wallet name)
  - `ORDERSEQ` (ordering)
  - `currencyUid` (FK to `CURRENCY.uid`)
  - `groupUid` (FK to `ASSETGROUP.uid`)
  - `CARD_DAY_FIN`, `CARD_DAY_PAY` (billing dates for card-type assets)
  - `IS_TRANS_EXPENSE`, `IS_CARD_AUTO_PAY` (flags for behavior)
  - `A_UTIME` (last update time)

### CURRENCY

- **Primary key**: `ID` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (VARCHAR, unique via `UNIQUE_IDX_CURRENCY_UID`)
- **Core columns**:
  - `NAME`, `ISO`, `MAIN_ISO`
  - `SYMBOL`, `SYMBOL_POSITION` (`P` or `S`)
  - `RATE` (exchange rate)
  - `IS_MAIN_CURRENCY`, `IS_SHOW`
  - `DECIMAL_POINT`
  - `ORDER_SEQ`

### ZCATEGORY

- **Primary key**: `ID` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT, unique via `UNIQUE_IDX_CATEGORY_UID`)
- **Core columns**:
  - `NAME`
  - `TYPE` (income/expense/etc.)
  - `STATUS`
  - `pUid` (parent category `uid` or `"0"`)
  - `ORDERSEQ`
  - `C_IS_DEL` (soft delete)
  - `C_UTIME` (last update time)

### INOUTCOME

- **Primary key**: `AID` (INTEGER)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT, unique via `UNIQUE_IDX_INOUTCOME_UID`)
- **Core relationships**:
  - `assetUid` → `ASSETS.uid`
  - `ctgUid` → `ZCATEGORY.uid`
  - `toAssetUid` → `ASSETS.uid` (for transfers)
  - `currencyUid` → `CURRENCY.uid`
- **Important columns**:
  - `DO_TYPE` (transaction type; mapped to Vaultix `DoType`)
  - `ZDATE` (transaction date, stored as VARCHAR/number)
  - `WDATE` (write date)
  - `ZMONEY` (amount)
  - `IN_ZMONEY` (counter-amount for transfers)
  - `AMOUNT_ACCOUNT` (normalized amount)
  - `ZCONTENT` (description/memo)
  - `MARK` (flags/starred status)
  - `IS_DEL` (soft delete)
  - `UTIME` (last update time)
  - `lat`, `lng` (location)
- **Indexes**:
  - `INOUTCOME_IDX2` on `DO_TYPE`
  - `INOUTCOME_IDX3` on `ZDATE`
  - `INOUTCOME_IDX6` on `UTIME`
  - `INOUTCOME_IDX7` on `assetUid`
  - `INOUTCOME_IDX8` on `ctgUid`
  - `INOUTCOME_IDX9` on `currencyUid`

### TAG

- **Primary key**: `id` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT, unique via `UNIQUE_IDX_TAG_UID`)
- **Columns**:
  - `name`
  - `orderSeq`
  - `isDel`
  - `utime`

### TX_TAG

- **Primary key**: `id` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT, unique via `UNIQUE_IDX_TX_TAG_UID`)
- **Relationships**:
  - `txUid` → `INOUTCOME.uid`
  - `tagUid` → `TAG.uid`
- **Columns**:
  - `objName` (optional label)
  - `orderSeq`
  - `isDel`
  - `utime`
- **Indexes**:
  - `TX_TAG_IDX1` on `txUid`

### BUDGET

- **Primary key**: `ID` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT)
- **Columns**:
  - `targetUid` (points to category or asset, depending on usage)
  - `DO_TYPE`
  - `PERIOD_TYPE`
  - `IS_TOTAL`
  - `IS_DEL`
  - `TRANSFER_TYPE`
  - `ORDER_SEQ`
  - `MODIFY_DATE`

### BUDGET_AMOUNT

- **Primary key**: `ID` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT)
- **Columns**:
  - `budgetUid` → `BUDGET.uid`
  - `AMOUNT`
  - `BUDGET_PERIOD`
  - `IS_DEL`
  - `MODIFY_DATE`

### REPEATTRANSACTION

- **Primary key**: `DEVICE_ID` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT)
- **Columns**:
  - `DO_TYPE`
  - `REPEAT_TYPE`
  - `assetUid`, `toAssetUid`, `ctgUid`, `currencyUid`
  - `AMOUNT_SUB`
  - `MEMO`, `PAYEE`
  - `END_DATE`, `NEXT_DATE`
  - `IS_DEL`, `MARK`, `USETIME`

### FAVTRANSACTION

- **Primary key**: `DEVICE_ID` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT)
- **Columns**:
  - `DO_TYPE`
  - `assetUid`, `toAssetUid`, `ctgUid`
  - `AMOUNT_SUB`
  - `currencyUid`
  - `MEMO`, `PAYEE`
  - `ORDERSEQ`
  - `IS_DEL`, `USETIME`, `MARK`

### MEMO

- **Primary key**: `id` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT)
- **Columns**:
  - `title`, `content`
  - `memoTime`, `memoDate`
  - `pinned`, `pinnedTime`
  - `orderSeq`
  - `color`
  - `isDel`, `utime`

### ZETC

- **Primary key**: `Z_PK` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT)
- **Columns**:
  - `ZDATATYPE`, `dataTypeKey`
  - `ZDATA`, `ZZDATA`, `ZZDATA1`, `ZZDATA2`
  - `E_UTIME`
  - `isDel`

### PHOTO

- **Primary key**: `DEVICE_ID` (INTEGER AUTOINCREMENT)
- **Logical key**: `uid` (TEXT)
- **Columns**:
  - `txUid` → `INOUTCOME.uid`
  - `FILE_SIZE`
  - `FILE_PATH`, `FILE_NAME`
  - `ORG_FILE_NAME`, `ORG_FILE_PATH`
  - `IS_DEL`, `USETIME`

### android_metadata

- Single-column table (`locale` TEXT) used by Android; Vaultix writes `en_US` when exporting.

